# Course Data Architecture — Audit & Fix Plan

## The Actual Problem

The sync endpoint ran but matched **0 of 22** records because:

| Source | ID format | Example |
|---|---|---|
| [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15) collection (old) | lowercase | `dccm`, `dmlt`, `mba-ha` |
| [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#17-35) collection (new) | UPPERCASE + trailing spaces | `DCCM`, `DMLT`, `MBA ` |

Case-insensitive matching + `.trim()` will fix this entirely.

## What's Duplicated / Broken Right Now

| File | Problem |
|---|---|
| [/app/admin/course-pricing/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/course-pricing/page.tsx) | Still imports [courseData.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/data/courseData.ts) (old hardcoded 22) |
| [/app/admin/finance/fees/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/finance/fees/page.tsx) | Old page, still uses [courseData.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/data/courseData.ts) |
| [/api/admin/course-pricing/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/course-pricing/route.ts) | Updated to use Program — but its page still uses old data |
| [/api/admin/fees/course/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/fees/course/route.ts) | Updated to use Program ✓ |
| [/api/public/courses/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/public/courses/route.ts) | Updated to use Program ✓ |
| [/api/public/course-pricing/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/public/course-pricing/route.ts) | Updated to use Program ✓ |
| [CoursePricingBadge](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/public/CoursePricing.tsx#45-86) | Fetches [/api/public/course-pricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/public/course-pricing) which reads Program ✓ |
| Sync endpoint | Fails silently due to case mismatch |

## The Fix (2 changes only)

### 1. Fix sync endpoint — case-insensitive + trim matching
In [/api/admin/courses/sync-pricing/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/courses/sync-pricing/route.ts):
```diff
- p.code?.toLowerCase() === cp.courseId?.toLowerCase()
+ p.code?.trim().toLowerCase() === cp.courseId?.trim().toLowerCase()
```

### 2. Delete the two dead duplicate pages
- [/app/admin/course-pricing/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/course-pricing/page.tsx) — still uses [courseData.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/data/courseData.ts). Dead route, remove it.
- [/app/admin/finance/fees/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/finance/fees/page.tsx) — old page, remove it.

## After Fix
1. Deploy sync endpoint fix
2. Call `https://ldmcollege.com/api/admin/courses/sync-pricing?secret=ldm2025sync`
3. All fees from CoursePricing → Program.pricing. Done.
